Ms. Crenshaw,
Thank you very much for the message.
I am very interested in the opportunity to talk to personnel from the Research Group at Enron.
Between the two days you suggest,
I prefer Wednesday 12/6.
Considering the two-hour time difference between California and Texas,
11:00 am Pacific time (1:00 pm your time) seems to be a good slot.
However, I am open most of the day on 12/6 so if some other time slot is prefered on your end, please let me know.
Thanks again.
I look forward to talking to you and your colleagues.
Jingming
On Tue, 28 Nov 2000 Shirley.Crenshaw@enron.com wrote:

Please let me know
